Spell-Like Abilities	KEY:Demon (Rutterkin) ~ Spell-Like Abilities				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Demon (Rutterkin) Race Trait.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At will-darkness, cause fear, telekinesis; 1/day-desecrate. Caster level 6th; save DC 10 + spell level.
